<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erberg<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, von
                        der sprüch <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ir zu mir meynt zu haben,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ir <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des rats zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
                        nehst <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> und ich den <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Heydenab<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> yecz gesandt hett, der hat mir gesagt, wie
                        er nach vil rede von <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, daz ich
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> von willkür eins
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> sein sülle
                            <expan>hiezwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>pfingst<ex>en</ex></expan> schierist</q>31.05.1422</note></app> vor
                            <expan>mein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> und den
                        reten zu Strawbing, und er sey zu Strawbing <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>
